      "title": "A robot to make Covid treatment easier",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A teddy robot that can be operated by remote control from a distance of about 300 meters and can give medicine and food to Covid patients as well as communicate with patients was donated to Panadura Basic Hospital today (08).",
        "This robot has been donated under Nilwala Electricity Pvt. Ltd.'s \"Vidusaviya Gamata Olyak\" program.",
        "The active director of the company Mr. Roshan Siriwardena handed over the teddy robot to Dr. Indrani Godakanda, Medical Superintendent of Panadura Basic Hospital."
      ],
